(71, 188, 0, 32, 1, 1585909069, 127, 7, 0, 0, 0, '<span class=\"size5\">这个屏幕锁的界面是这样的</span>：<img src=\"upload/attach/202004/03/180826lng8hc8x2h06h4gm.png\">\r<br><span class=\"size4\">拖进OD后找易语言的文本比较，Ctrl+F找 test eax,3</span>\r<br><span class=\"size4\">下个断点</span>\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/03/180830znyp8kpjqh88fqc5.png\">\r<br><span class=\"size4\">然后输入假码，程序成功断下来</span>\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/03/180835h1gt7ltb9xt9qne9.png\">\r<br>F8往下走后发现一串密码\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/03/180843bcc9shsa43mxb549.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/03/180843gcjd8vp9p4c92mcc.png\">\r<br><span class=\"size4\">再除以序列号</span>\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/03/180843ef31ll1611k45n4z.png\">\r<br><span class=\"size4\">发现结果是30，所以，密码就是序列号*30</span>\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/03/180846euw9qkbmv4qbmo0b.png\">\r<br><span class=\"size4\">然后他就解锁了</span>\r<br><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">\r<br></span>\r<br><span class=\"size5\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">（ps：小白初识OD，大佬嘴下留情！！）</span></span>\r<br><p class=\"imagelist\"><a href=\"upload/attach/202004/03/180826lng8hc8x2h06h4gm.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202004/03/180826lng8hc8x2h06h4gm.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/03/180826lng8hc8x2h06h4gm.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"0\"  style=\"width: 800px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202004/03/180830znyp8kpjqh88fqc5.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202004/03/180830znyp8kpjqh88fqc5.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/03/180830znyp8kpjqh88fqc5.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"0\"  style=\"width: 800px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202004/03/180835h1gt7ltb9xt9qne9.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202004/03/180835h1gt7ltb9xt9qne9.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/03/180835h1gt7ltb9xt9qne9.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"0\"  style=\"width: 800px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202004/03/180843bcc9shsa43mx