(97, 260, 0, 32, 1, 1587460840, 127, 3, 0, 0, 0, '花指令的作用的话，就是把代码变得十分复杂，对付一些静态分析有很好的效果，那么\r<br>如何加上花指令呢？这类以易语言为例子，依次点开工具——系统配置——安全\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/171922bwszh6z7h76chx0c.png\">\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/171922hujrwacxjxwmjujz.png\">\r<br>然后选择花指令的强度即可，加上去之后反汇编就是这个样子的了\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/171923jyrd885duvxuc6ps.png\">\r<br>是不是变得看都看不懂了，这样就实现了一些反调试的效果\r<br><p class=\"imagelist\"><a href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/171922bwszh6z7h76chx0c.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/171922bwszh6z7h76chx0c.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/171922bwszh6z7h76chx0c.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"0\"  style=\"width: 800px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/171922hujrwacxjxwmjujz.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/171922hujrwacxjxwmjujz.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/171922hujrwacxjxwmjujz.png\" width=\"407\" height=\"0\"  style=\"width: 800px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/171923jyrd885duvxuc6ps.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/171923jyrd885duvxuc6ps.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/171923jyrd885duvxuc6ps.png\" width=\"665\" height=\"0\"  style=\"width: 800px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a></p>', '花指令的作用的话，就是把代码变得十分复杂，对付一些静态分析有很好的效果，那么\r<br>如何加上花指令呢？这类以易语言为例子，依次点开工具——系统配置——安全\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/171922bwszh6z7h76chx0c.png\">\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/171922hujrwacxjxwmjujz.png\">\r<br>然后选择花指令的强度即可，加上去之后反汇编就是这个样子的了\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/171923jyrd885duvxuc6ps.png\">\r<br>是不是变得看都看不懂了，这样就实现了一些反调试的效果\r<br><p class=\"imagelist\"><a href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/171922bwszh6z7h76chx0c.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/171922bwszh6z7h76chx0c.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/171922bwszh6z7h76chx0c.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"0\"  style=\"width: 800px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/171922hujrwacxjxwmjujz.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/171922hujrwacxjxwmjujz.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/171922hujrwacxjxwmjujz.png\" width=\"407\" height=\"0\"  style=\"width: 800px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/171923jyrd885duvxuc6ps.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/171923jyrd885duvxuc6ps.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/171923jyrd885duvxuc6ps.png\" width=\"665\" height=\"0\"  style=\"width: 800px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a></p>'),
(98, 261, 0, 32, 1, 1587461274, 127, 2, 0, 0, 0, '对于破解者来说，文本字符串无疑是个重要的参考对象，所以，只要将字符串给隐藏起来，\r<br>让破解者不会轻易拿到字符串的话，就能增加软件的安全性\r<br>具体的隐藏方法有很多，这就不一一列举了（比如花指令啥的），这是隐藏字符串之前的效果和隐藏之后的效果\r<br>隐藏前：\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/172657q1iddiedbbb14bjd.png\">\r<br>隐藏后：\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/172658grbr1x0uhbh2t17j.png\">\r<br>没了字符串，参考也没了，就能档住一些破解者\r<br><p class=\"imagelist\"><a href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/172657q1iddiedbbb14bjd.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/172657q1iddiedbbb14bjd.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/172657q1iddiedbbb14bjd.png\" width=\"466\" height=\"0\" ></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/172658grbr1x0uhbh2t17j.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/172658grbr1x0uhbh2t17j.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/172658grbr1x0uhbh2t17j.png\" width=\"459\" height=\"0\" ></a></p>', '对于破解者来说，文本字符串无疑是个重要的参考对象，所以，只要将字符串给隐藏起来，\r<br>让破解者不会轻易拿到字符串的话，就能增加软件的安全性\r<br>具体的隐藏方法有很多，这就不一一列举了（比如花指令啥的），这是隐藏字符串之前的效果和隐藏之后的效果\r<br>隐藏前：\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/172657q1iddiedbbb14bjd.png\">\r<br>隐藏后：\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/172658grbr1x0uhbh2t17j.png\">\r<br>没了字符串，参考也没了，就能档住一些破解者\r<br><p class=\"imagelist\"><a href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/172657q1iddiedbbb14bjd.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/172657q1iddiedbbb14bjd.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/172657q1iddiedbbb14bjd.png\" width=\"466\" height=\"0\" ></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/172658grbr1x0uhbh2t17j.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/172658grbr1x0uhbh2t17j.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/172658grbr1x0uhbh2t17j.png\" width=\"459\" height=\"0\" ></a></p>'),
(99, 262, 0, 32, 1, 1587461812, 127, 2, 0, 0, 0, '如果要破解软件，那么肯定会用到调试器，那么直接把调试器干掉，破解者就没法下手了，从而\r<br>达到保护软件的效果。\r<br>那么，怎么检测调试器呢，这里提供个思路：检测进程，易语言可以这样写\r<br>通过取到OD的进程来判断是否运行调试器\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/173511xafiyyzja3jka35s.png\">\r<br>编译出来后的效果\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/173517us68q794s97zs9dn.png\">\r<br>这样就干掉了调试器，从而让一些破解者选择放弃。\r<br><p class=\"imagelist\"><a href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/173511xafiyyzja3jka35s.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/173511xafiyyzja3jka35s.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/173511xafiyyzja3jka35s.png\" width=\"427\" height=\"0\" ></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/173517us68q794s97zs9dn.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/173517us68q794s97zs9dn.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/173517us68q794s97zs9dn.png\" width=\"640\" height=\"0\" ></a></p>', '如果要破解软件，那么肯定会用到调试器，那么直接把调试器干掉，破解者就没法下手了，从而\r<br>达到保护软件的效果。\r<br>那么，怎么检测调试器呢，这里提供个思路：检测进程，易语言可以这样写\r<br>通过取到OD的进程来判断是否运行调试器\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/173511xafiyyzja3jka35s.png\">\r<br>编译出来后的效果\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/173517us68q794s97zs9dn.png\">\r<br>这样就干掉了调试器，从而让一些破解者选择放弃。\r<br><p class=\"imagelist\"><a href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/173511xafiyyzja3jka35s.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/173511xafiyyzja3jka35s.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/173511xafiyyzja3jka35s.png\" width=\"427\" height=\"0\" ></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/173517us68q794s97zs9dn.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202004/21/173517us68q794s97zs9dn.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202004/21/173517us68q794s97zs9dn.png\" width=\"640\" height=\"0\" ></a></p>'),
