(122, 310, 0, 74, 1, 1589592573, 127, 1, 0, 0, 0, '<span class=\"size5\">前言：</span>\r<br><span class=\"size5\">吃完饭，开始进行了我易语言生活，看着这灰白的界面，我不由得感叹了一声。</span>\r<br><img src=\"200,200\" alt=\"http://img0.imgtn.bdimg.com/it/u=2776399318,240890168&amp;fm=26&amp;gp=0.jpg\" title=\"http://img0.imgtn.bdimg.com/it/u=2776399318,240890168&amp;fm=26&amp;gp=0.jpg\">\r<br>\r<br><span class=\"size5\">应该很多人吐槽易语言界面丑吧</span>\r<br><span class=\"size5\">很多人还不知道这个界面怎么下载</span>\r<br><span class=\"size5\">于是给你找来了</span>\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202005/16/092530v6x0z0q0rau42vq1.png\">\r<br><span class=\"size5\">看着这好看的界面，我心情无比畅快</span>\r<br><img alt=\"http://wx4.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/ceeb653ely1fnego9whacj205k04o74y.jpg\" title=\"http://wx4.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/ceeb653ely1fnego9whacj205k04o74y.jpg\" src=\"200,168\">\r<br><span class=\"size5\">\r<br></span>\r<br><span class=\"size5\">教程地址：</span><span style=\"color: rgb(27,;\"><span><a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/av94039966\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av94039966</a></span></span>\r<br><span class=\"size5\">注：本教程视频地址来自于转载</span>\r<br><span class=\"size5\">请务必看完教程</span>\r<br><p class=\"imagelist\"><a href=\"upload/attach/202005/16/092530v6x0z0q0rau42vq1.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202005/16/092530v6x0z0q0rau42vq1.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202005/16/092530v6x0z0q0rau42vq1.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"0\"  style=\"width: 800px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a></p>', '<span class=\"size5\">前言：</span>\r<br><span class=\"size5\">吃完饭，开始进行了我易语言生活，看着这灰白的界面，我不由得感叹了一声。</span>\r<br><img src=\"200,200\" alt=\"http://img0.imgtn.bdimg.com/it/u=2776399318,240890168&amp;fm=26&amp;gp=0.jpg\" title=\"http://img0.imgtn.bdimg.com/it/u=2776399318,240890168&amp;fm=26&amp;gp=0.jpg\">\r<br>\r<br><span class=\"size5\">应该很多人吐槽易语言界面丑吧</span>\r<br><span class=\"size5\">很多人还不知道这个界面怎么下载</span>\r<br><span class=\"size5\">于是给你找来了</span>\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202005/16/092530v6x0z0q0rau42vq1.png\">\r<br><span class=\"size5\">看着