(134, 330, 0, 134, 1, 1590752342, 127, 1, 0, 0, 0, '我们来讲一讲Proxmark3,Proxmark3是一款最初由Jonathan Westhues发布的一款用于测试高低频RFID的开源硬件，用于读写模拟克隆嗅探RFID卡。\r<br>我使用的是一款国内的Proxmark3 Easy，如下图。圆形线圈是低频卡（ID）的读卡线圈，上侧是高频卡（IC）的读卡线圈。<p class=\"imagelist\"><a href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/193508hs83cvz08mh8evma.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/193508hs83cvz08mh8evma.jpg\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202005/29/193508hs83cvz08mh8evma.jpg\" width=\"282\" height=\"0\" ></a></p>', '我们来讲一讲Proxmark3,Proxmark3是一款最初由Jonathan Westhues发布的一款用于测试高低频RFID的开源硬件，用于读写模拟克隆嗅探RFID卡。\r<br>我使用的是一款国内的Proxmark3 Easy，如下图。圆形线圈是低频卡（ID）的读卡线圈，上侧是高频卡（IC）的读卡线圈。<p class=\"imagelist\"><a href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/193508hs83cvz08mh8evma.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/193508hs83cvz08mh8evma.jpg\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202005/29/193508hs83cvz08mh8evma.jpg\" width=\"282\" height=\"0\" ></a></p>'),
(134, 331, 0, 134, 0, 1590753542, 127, 0, 0, 0, 0, '首先我们在Linux进行编译固件和客户端。', '首先我们在Linux进行编译固件和客户端。'),
(134, 332, 0, 134, 0, 1590753675, 127, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'git clone https://github.com/RfidResearchGroup/proxmark3', 'git clone https://github.com/RfidResearchGroup/proxmark3'),
(134, 333, 0, 134, 0, 1590753868, 127, 0, 0, 0, 0, '安装依赖 sudo apt-get install --no-install-recommends git ca-certificates build-essential pkg-config \\ libreadline-dev gcc-arm-none-eabi libnewlib-dev qtbase5-dev libbluetooth-dev', '安装依赖 sudo apt-get install --no-install-recommends git ca-certificates build-essential pkg-config \\ libreadline-dev gcc-arm-none-eabi libnewlib-dev qtbase5-dev libbluetooth-dev'),
(134, 334, 0, 134, 0, 1590754100, 127, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'cd进proxmark3目录，执行命令编译。make clean &amp;&amp; make PLATFORM=PM3OTHER', 'cd进proxmark3目录，执行命令编译。make clean &amp;&amp; make PLATFORM=PM3OTHER'),
(134, 335, 0, 134, 0, 1590754325, 127, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'cd进proxmark3下的client目录。执行./proxmark3 /dev/ttyACM0 --flash --unlock-bootloader --image proxmark3的绝对路径/bootrom/obj/bootrom.elf --image proxmark3的绝对路径/armsrc/obj/fullimage.elf', 'cd进proxmark3下的client目录。执行./proxmark3 /dev/ttyACM0 --flash --unlock-bootloader --image proxmark3的绝对路径/bootrom/obj/bootrom.elf --image proxmark3的绝对路径/armsrc/obj/fullimage.elf'),
(134, 336, 0, 134, 0, 1590755008, 127, 1, 0, 0, 0, '6#是刷新PM3固件，刷新完以后cd进proxmark3目录下的client目录执行./proxmark3 /dev/ttyACM0命令，来进行客户端交互操作。\r<br>\r<br><p class=\"imagelist\"><a href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/202028uzlyllpgziqdb5pu.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/202028uzlyllpgziqdb5pu.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202005/29/202028uzlyllpgziqdb5pu.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"0\"  style=\"width: 800px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a></p>', '6#是刷新PM3固件，刷新完以后cd进proxmark3目录下的client目录执行./proxmark3 /dev/ttyACM0命令，来进行客户端交互操作。\r<br>\r<br><p class=\"imagelist\"><a href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/202028uzlyllpgziqdb5pu.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/202028uzlyllpgziqdb5pu.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202005/29/202028uzlyllpgziqdb5pu.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"0\"  style=\"width: 800px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a></p>'),
(134, 337, 0, 134, 0, 1590755150, 127, 1, 0, 0, 0, '然后我们把需要读取数据的IC卡放在，高频天线位上。<p class=\"imagelist\"><a href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/202529lmsh799jmht63h7p.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/202529lmsh799jmht63h7p.jpg\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202005/29/202529lmsh799jmht63h7p.jpg\" width=\"282\" height=\"0\" ></a></p>', '然后我们把需要读取数据的IC卡放在，高频天线位上。<p class=\"imagelist\"><a href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/202529lmsh799jmht63h7p.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/202529lmsh799jmht63h7p.jpg\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202005/29/202529lmsh799jmht63h7p.jpg\" width=\"282\" height=\"0\" ></a></p>'),
(134, 338, 0, 1, 0, 1590756866, 127, 0, 0, 0, 0, '大佬', '大佬'),
(134, 339, 0, 134, 0, 1590758550, 127, 1, 0, 0, 0, '然后我们可以通过执行lf search来确认是否是低频卡以及类型或hf search来确认是否是高频卡以及类型。\r<br>\r<br><p class=\"imagelist\"><a href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/211712uhuu4hu24604vl0w.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/211712uhuu4hu24604vl0w.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202005/29/211712uhuu4hu24604vl0w.png\" width=\"534\" height=\"0\" ></a></p>', '然后我们可以通过执行lf search来确认是否是低频卡以及类型或hf search来确认是否是高频卡以及类型。\r<br>\r<br><p class=\"imagelist\"><a href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/211712uhuu4hu24604vl0w.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/211712uhuu4hu24604vl0w.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202005/29/211712uhuu4hu24604vl0w.png\" width=\"534\" height=\"0\" ></a></p>');
