(134, 340, 0, 134, 0, 1590759473, 127, 2, 0, 0, 0, '使用hf mf chk *1 ? t命令来检索默认密钥到内存。如图发现只有开头是默认密钥，我们需要进行下一步得到全部的密钥才能对全部的扇区进行读写。\r<br>\r<br><p class=\"imagelist\"><a href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/213347frdh4jqn4scsqaat.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/213347frdh4jqn4scsqaat.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202005/29/213347frdh4jqn4scsqaat.png\" width=\"463\" height=\"0\" ></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/213349k84widyd6nqv631t.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/213349k84widyd6nqv631t.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202005/29/213349k84widyd6nqv631t.png\" width=\"463\" height=\"0\" ></a></p>', '使用hf mf chk *1 ? t命令来检索默认密钥到内存。如图发现只有开头是默认密钥，我们需要进行下一步得到全部的密钥才能对全部的扇区进行读写。\r<br>\r<br><p class=\"imagelist\"><a href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/213347frdh4jqn4scsqaat.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/213347frdh4jqn4scsqaat.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202005/29/213347frdh4jqn4scsqaat.png\" width=\"463\" height=\"0\" ></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/213349k84widyd6nqv631t.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/213349k84widyd6nqv631t.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202005/29/213349k84widyd6nqv631t.png\" width=\"463\" height=\"0\" ></a></p>'),
(134, 341, 0, 134, 0, 1590761070, 127, 1, 0, 0, 0, '运行hf mf autopwn自动利用卡片漏洞或知一密求多密自动攻击并导出卡内数据。后期分析不再研究，金额卡不要碰一碰。法律责任与我无关。科普。\r<br>\r<br><p class=\"imagelist\"><a href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/220220brzr6kbkrwh0jzrk.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/220220brzr6kbkrwh0jzrk.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202005/29/220220brzr6kbkrwh0jzrk.png\" width=\"463\" height=\"0\" ></a></p>', '运行hf mf autopwn自动利用卡片漏洞或知一密求多密自动攻击并导出卡内数据。后期分析不再研究，金额卡不要碰一碰。法律责任与我无关。科普。\r<br>\r<br><p class=\"imagelist\"><a href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/220220brzr6kbkrwh0jzrk.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202005/29/220220brzr6kbkrwh0jzrk.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202005/29/220220brzr6kbkrwh0jzrk.png\" width=\"463\" height=\"0\" ></a></p>'),
