(192, 471, 0, 32, 1, 1597405454, 127, 8, 0, 0, 0, '我们知道，VMProtect是一款商用的虚拟机保护壳，那么他的重点就是他的虚拟保护——vm\r<br>但是他的VM有些漏洞，一般情况下，我们写代码是这样添加标志位的——用易语言举例\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193525wbruttf8rdy8juxz.png\">\r<br>然后放到VMP里，她会自动识别\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193525jgekqsbssgswrwks.png\">\r<br>编译结束后，就已经对关键代码进行保护了，我们下Megbox找按钮事件对比下：\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193526x4u7uofe1o7u1kzc.png\">\r<br>F8走出来，可以看到区别\r<br>加密前，简单明了\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193527os14tneunednwdh8.png\">\r<br>加密后，V的亲妈都不认识\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193526z0m6piwk6gqq1456.png\">\r<br>是不是这样就束手无策了呢？并不是，VM是有缺点的，像刚刚那种写法（图1），VM的地方是不全的。\r<br>所以，我们跳到地址00401000，然后在几个RETN出下断点。\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193527jflryjpppxglj8pl.png\">\r<br>然后点击按钮\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193528io1orsu1utoy8ti1.png\">\r<br>程序断下来后，把寄存器EAX的值改成0，判断就过了\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193528rcv2mp3l393rrzwj.png\">\r<br>这样，就破开了加了VM的软件了。（当然，这种只是比较简单的）\r<br>\r<br><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">\r<br></span>\r<br><span class=\"size6\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">PS：请问怎么写补丁来改EAX的值啊，在线求解答。</span></span>\r<br><p class=\"imagelist\"><a href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193525wbruttf8rdy8juxz.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193525wbruttf8rdy8juxz.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193525wbruttf8rdy8juxz.png\" width=\"487\" height=\"0\" ></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193525jgekqsbssgswrwks.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193525jgekqsbssgswrwks.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193525jgekqsbssgswrwks.png\" width=\"606\" height=\"0\" ></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193526x4u7uofe1o7u1kzc.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193526x4u7uofe1o7u1kzc.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193526x4u7uofe1o7u1kzc.png\" width=\"317\" height=\"0\" ></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193526z0m6piwk6gqq1456.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193526z0m6piwk6gqq1456.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193526z0m6piwk6gqq1456.png\" width=\"696\" height=\"0\" ></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193527os14tneunednwdh8.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193527os14tneunednwdh8.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193527os14tneunednwdh8.png\" width=\"689\" height=\"0\" ></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193527jflryjpppxglj8pl.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193527jflryjpppxglj8pl.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193527jflryjpppxglj8pl.png\" width=\"648\" height=\"0\" ></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193528io1orsu1utoy8ti1.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193528io1orsu1utoy8ti1.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193528io1orsu1utoy8ti1.png\" width=\"799\" height=\"0\" ></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193528rcv2mp3l393rrzwj.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193528rcv2mp3l393rrzwj.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193528rcv2mp3l393rrzwj.png\" width=\"720\" height=\"0\" ></a></p>', '我们知道，VMProtect是一款商用的虚拟机保护壳，那么他的重点就是他的虚拟保护——vm\r<br>但是他的VM有些漏洞，一般情况下，我们写代码是这样添加标志位的——用易语言举例\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193525wbruttf8rdy8juxz.png\">\r<br>然后放到VMP里，她会自动识别\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193525jgekqsbssgswrwks.png\">\r<br>编译结束后，就已经对关键代码进行保护了，我们下Megbox找按钮事件对比下：\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193526x4u7uofe1o7u1kzc.png\">\r<br>F8走出来，可以看到区别\r<br>加密前，简单明了\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193527os14tneunednwdh8.png\">\r<br>加密后，V的亲妈都不认识\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193526z0m6piwk6gqq1456.png\">\r<br>是不是这样就束手无策了呢？并不是，VM是有缺点的，像刚刚那种写法（图1），VM的地方是不全的。\r<br>所以，我们跳到地址00401000，然后在几个RETN出下断点。\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193527jflryjpppxglj8pl.png\">\r<br>然后点击按钮\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193528io1orsu1utoy8ti1.png\">\r<br>程序断下来后，把寄存器EAX的值改成0，判断就过了\r<br><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193528rcv2mp3l393rrzwj.png\">\r<br>这样，就破开了加了VM的软件了。（当然，这种只是比较简单的）\r<br>\r<br><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">\r<br></span>\r<br><span class=\"size6\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">PS：请问怎么写补丁来改EAX的值啊，在线求解答。</span></span>\r<br><p class=\"imagelist\"><a href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193525wbruttf8rdy8juxz.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193525wbruttf8rdy8juxz.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193525wbruttf8rdy8juxz.png\" width=\"487\" height=\"0\" ></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193525jgekqsbssgswrwks.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193525jgekqsbssgswrwks.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193525jgekqsbssgswrwks.png\" width=\"606\" height=\"0\" ></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193526x4u7uofe1o7u1kzc.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193526x4u7uofe1o7u1kzc.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193526x4u7uofe1o7u1kzc.png\" width=\"317\" height=\"0\" ></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193526z0m6piwk6gqq1456.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193526z0m6piwk6gqq1456.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193526z0m6piwk6gqq1456.png\" width=\"696\" height=\"0\" ></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193527os14tneunednwdh8.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193527os14tneunednwdh8.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193527os14tneunednwdh8.png\" width=\"689\" height=\"0\" ></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193527jflryjpppxglj8pl.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193527jflryjpppxglj8pl.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193527jflryjpppxglj8pl.png\" width=\"648\" height=\"0\" ></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193528io1orsu1utoy8ti1.png\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193528io1orsu1utoy8ti1.png\"><img src=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193528io1orsu1utoy8ti1.png\" width=\"799\" height=\"0\" ></a><br><a href=\"upload/attach/202008/14/193528rcv2mp3l393rrzwj.png\" target=\"_bl