INSERT INTO `bbs_post` (`tid`, `pid`, `fid`, `uid`, `isfirst`, `create_date`, `userip`, `images`, `files`, `doctype`, `quotepid`, `message`, `message_fmt`) VALUES
(234, 600, 0, 2, 1, 1619871904, 127, 1, 1, 0, 0, '<p><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;font-size:16px;overflow-wrap: break-word;color:#ff0000;overflow-wrap: break-word;\">【全网最简单的教程】PCQQ防撤回制作教程（版本无重大变化下，同样适用于Tim）</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"font-size:16px;overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif;color:#ff0000;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700;\">20210226终于有一点时间了，更新一下通用查找替换码，适配任意版本的PCQQ</span></span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"font-size:16px;overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif;color:#ff0000;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700;\">(已修复winhex提示临时路径不能写入的问题；提示写保护--对于无法保存的，可以把文件先另存到桌面，然后将新文件拖动到原文件目录，替换，完事。)</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"/><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"font-size:16px;overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700;color:#ff0000;overflow-wrap: break-word;\">前言：</span></span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;font-size:16px;overflow-wrap: break-word;\">熟悉TMTT的朋友应该都知道，我每次发贴都是内容比较多的，是为了把帖子步骤尽量完善详细化，但是同样不可避免的造成帖子篇幅太长了，所以特别写了这一贴。<br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;\"/>全网最简单的PCQQ防撤回制作教程，送给想要自己制作防撤回功能的朋友们【<span style=\"color:#ff0000;overflow-wrap: break-word;\">只想把最简单的/最好的送给你们，爱你们的必兮相语</span><img src=\"https://static.52pojie.cn/static/image/smiley/default/shy.gif\" smilieid=\"8\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;\"/>】<br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"color:#ff0000;overflow-wrap: break-word;\">一、何为简单</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;\"/>本教程只需要最简单的<span style=\"color:#ff0000;overflow-wrap: break-word;\">3步</span>即可完成。<br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;\"/>1、打开<br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"color:#ff0000;overflow-wrap: break-word;\">2、替换</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;\"/>3、保存</span></p><p><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;font-size:16px;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;font-size:16px;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;font-size:16px;overflow-wrap: break-word;color:#ff0000;overflow-wrap: break-word;\">二、最终效果：</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;font-size:16px;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;font-size:16px;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;font-size:16px;overflow-wrap: break-word;color:#ff0000;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><a href=\"upload/attach/202105/2_UM8RYE553W9UCX3.gif\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"upload/attach/202105/2_UM8RYE553W9UCX3.gif