(235, 602, 0, 2, 1, 1619874952, 127, 0, 1, 0, 0, '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">当时在做网页内容读取的时候突然来的灵感，文本和图片都可以从网页读取的话，就可以利用这一点进行远程控制。</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"/><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"font-size:24px;overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif;color:#ff0000;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700;\">第一步：</span></span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">首先呢，需要有一个博客，把更新信息输在里面，然后用易去读取这个更新信息，进行检查更新，如下：</span></p><p><img id=\"aimg_2230958\" aid=\"2230958\" src=\"https://attach.52pojie.cn/forum/202103/13/233758bepjpcbncf79cj71.png\" zoomfile=\"https://attach.52pojie.cn/forum/202103/13/233758bepjpcbncf79cj71.png\" file=\"https://attach.52pojie.cn/forum/202103/13/233758bepjpcbncf79cj71.png\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"684\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" height=\"492\" initialized=\"true\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:24px;overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif;color:#ff0000;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700;\">第二步：</span></span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">判断需不需要更新，这些东西就不多说了，推荐这些数据放在博客里面，好改。</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">接着就是把更新文件放在网络上。</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">更新原理：先把文件转成图</span><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">片，然后把图片上传到图库，获取链接以后，把链接放在博客上，客户端读取，然后拼接数据。如图：</span></p><p><img id=\"aimg_2230959\" aid=\"2230959\" src=\"https://attach.52pojie.cn/forum/202103/13/233809qlckotvonvczocnv.png\" zoomfile=\"https://attach.52pojie.cn/forum/202103/13/233809qlckotvonvczocnv.png\" file=\"https://attach.52pojie.cn/forum/202103/13/233809qlckotvonvczocnv.png\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"870\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" initialized=\"true\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p><br/></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">当时在做网页内容读取的时候突然来的灵感，文本和图片都可以从网页读取的话，就可以利用这一点进行远程控制。</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"/><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68