(265, 660, 0, 2, 1, 1620882216, 127, 0, 1, 0, 0, '<p><img src=\"https://att.125.la/data/attachment/forum/202105/07/155630x606jc2jqef22z28.gif\"/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\">去年有人找我说想研究个自动画画软件，刚好那段时间有空，就研究了下</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\">效果不是打印式一点一点画的，看动图就知道（图片没有加速）</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\">这是当时的成品贴，很多人要求开源，就整理了下开个源</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"color:#ff0000;overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\">自动绘画工具-发呆神器</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><a href=\"https://bbs.125.la/forum.php?mod=viewthread&tid=14653431\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 102, 153); text-decoration-line: underline; font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" _href=\"https://bbs.125.la/forum.php?mod=viewthread&tid=14653431\">https://bbs.125.la/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=14653431</a><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;font-size:18px;overflow-wrap: break-word;\">使用方法很简单</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;font-size:18px;overflow-wrap: break-word;\">1、打开电脑上的画板工具/用本程序启动电脑上的画板工具</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;font-size:18px;overflow-wrap: break-word;\">2、手动选好画笔颜色/粗细/类型等</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;font-size:18px;overflow-wrap: break-word;\">3、按照程序上的提示移动鼠标到画板某个位置后按下快捷键</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;font-size:18px;overflow-wrap: break-word;\">4、再次按下快捷键=暂停/恢复</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\">这里说下缺点</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\">1、画画期间不能动鼠标</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\">2、超出画板范围出错</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\">3、没法停止，只能强制</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\">4、不支持颜色</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\">5、二值化算法不够好</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\">之所以不做内存画法是因为技术有限，画板工具每个版本地址都不一样，不然就要录入很多版本的地址</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\">以上说的缺点有能力也可以自己填坑。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p>', '<p><img src=\"https://att.125.la/data/attachment/forum/202105/07/155630x606jc2jqef22z28.gif\"/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\">去年有人找我说想研究个自动画画软件，刚好那段时间有空，就研究了下</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\">效果不是打印式一点一点画的，看动图就知道（图片没有加速）</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\">这是当时的成品贴，很多人要求开源，就整理了下开个源</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"color:#ff0000;overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma, &quo