(302, 781, 0, 109, 1, 1626751686, 127, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">由github一位作者开发的检测软件，对win7系统友好，可以在win7系统下检测是否有支持升级的硬件条件，很可惜我的老电脑不支持升级，刚才发忘记带版本号https://wacr.lanzoui.com/iZzlKqphysf</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">新版本已经更新，原作者地址https://github.com/rcmaehl/WhyNotWin11/releases</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">转换的蓝奏云地址v2.2.4.0版本</span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);overflow-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(194, 236, 178);font-family:Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, 新宋体, sans-serif;overflow-wrap: break-word;\">https://wacr.lanzoui.com/ibXxzqruuwf</span><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">WhyNotWin11_x86&nbsp;</span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);overflow-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(194, 236, 178);font-family:Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, 新宋体, sans-serif;overflow-wrap: break-word;\">https://wacr.lanzoui.com/i7RGcqruuyh</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color:rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family:none; font-size:14px;\">由github一位作者开发的检测软件，对win7系统友好，可以在win7系统下检测是否有支持升级的硬件条件，很可惜我的老电脑不支持升级，刚才发忘记带版本号https://wacr.lanzoui.com/iZzlKqphysf</span><br style=\"color:rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family:none; font-size:14px;\" /><span style=\"color:rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family:none; font-size:14px;\">新版本已经更新，原作者地址https://github.com/rcmaehl/WhyNotWin11/releases</span><br style=\"color:rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family:none; font-size:14px;\" /><span style=\"color:rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family:none; font-size:14px;\">转换的蓝奏云地址v2.2.4.0版本</span><span style=\"font-family:none; font-size:14px; color:rgb(63, 63, 63); background-color:rgb(194, 236, 178);\">https://wacr.lanzoui.com/ibXxzqruuwf</span><br style=\"color:rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family:none; font-size:14px;\" /><span style=\"color:rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family:none; font-size:14px;\">WhyNotWin11_x86&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:none; font-size:14px; color:rgb(63, 63, 63); background-color:rgb(194, 236, 178);\">https://wacr.lanzoui.com/i7RGcqruuyh</spa